strength almost as inspiring as the chain of volcanoes in which it makes it's
home.  The massive blocks of basalt that form the structure nearly boggle the
mind, such are their incredible size and weight.  The narrow, little-used trail
at your feet that leads to this place from the south now ends to the north at
the foot of a gigantic series of steps that span the height of the ziggurat.  
